heading: 2. The 29th day of January 2020 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 29th day of January 2020 is appointed as the day on which the 
Migration of Participating Securities Act 2019 (No. 50 of 2019) shall come 
into operation. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal 

29 January, 2020. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 4th February, 2020.
